凯西·马斯格雷夫斯 (Kacey Musgraves) 宣布新专辑《Deeper Well》并分享​​主打单曲https://www.nme.com/news/music/kacey-musgraves-announces-new-album-deeper-well-and-shares-leads-single-3584616?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=kacey-musgraves-announces-新专辑 Deeper Well 和 Shares Leads 单曲Anagricel DuranThu, 08 Feb 2024 19:31:21 +0000 Music NewsNewsCountryPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3584616 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kacey-Musgraves.-Credit_-Kelly-Christine-Sutton.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="凯西·马斯格雷夫斯。图片来源：凯莉·克里斯汀·萨顿" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kacey-Musgraves.-Credit_-Kelly-Christine-Sutton.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kacey-Musgraves.-Credit_-Kelly-Christine-Sutton-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kacey-Musgraves.-Credit_-Kelly-Christine-Sutton-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kacey-Musgraves.-Credit_-Kelly-Christine-Sutton-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kacey-Musgraves.-Credit_-Kelly-Christine-Sutton-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kacey-Musgraves.-Credit_-Kelly-Christine-Sutton-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “有时你会到达十字路口。风改变方向。你曾经被吸引的东西不再具有同样的吸引力”</p><p>凯西<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kacey-musgraves-announces-new-album-deeper-well-and-shares-leads-single-3584616">·穆斯格雷夫斯 (Kacey Musgraves) 宣布新专辑《Deeper Well》并分享​​主打单曲后，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kacey-Musgraves.-Credit_-Kelly-Christine-Sutton.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="凯西·马斯格雷夫斯。图片来源：凯莉·克里斯汀·萨顿" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kacey-Musgraves.-Credit_-Kelly-Christine-Sutton.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kacey-Musgraves.-Credit_-Kelly-Christine-Sutton-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kacey-Musgraves.-Credit_-Kelly-Christine-Sutton-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kacey-Musgraves.-Credit_-Kelly-Christine-Sutton-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kacey-Musgraves.-Credit_-Kelly-Christine-Sutton-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kacey-Musgraves.-Credit_-Kelly-Christine-Sutton-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/kacey-musgraves">凯西·穆斯格雷夫斯 (Kacey Musgraves)</a>宣布了她的新专辑《Deeper Well》，并分享了该唱片的同名主打单曲。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/kacey-musgraves-star-crossed-review-3040734">凯西·马斯格雷夫斯（Kacey Musgraves）——《星辰变》评论：对心碎的有力而诚实的描述</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位七次获得格莱美奖的创作歌手将于 3 月 15 日通过 Interscope/MCA Nashville 发行她的第六张录音室唱片。 “更深的井”可<a href="https://kaceymusgraves.komi.io/">在此处进行预保存/预订</a>。</p><p>这张专辑由马斯格雷夫斯与她的长期合作者丹尼尔·塔西安（Daniel Tashian）和伊恩·菲丘克（Ian Fitchuk）共同制作。据新闻稿称，《Deeper Well》的灵感来自于纽约市格林威治村的活力及其丰富的音乐历史，新专辑的很大一部分是在传奇的 Electric Lady Studios 录制的。</p><p> “我一直在寻找一些不同的环境能源，而电动女士拥有最好的魔力。伟大的鬼魂。”马斯格雷夫斯说道。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Kacey Musgraves - Deeper Well（官方音乐视频）" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/TGkMYMxi-hw?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>这位歌手还分享了专辑的主打歌，这是其主打单曲。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kacey-musgraves-teases-new-music-at-grammys-2024-3582688">马斯格雷夫斯于上周末（2 月 4 日）在 2024 年格莱美颁奖典礼上预告了这首新歌</a>。谈到这首歌，这位歌手说：“有时你会到达十字路口。风改变方向。你曾经被吸引的东西不再具有同样的吸引力。你会偏离轨道，但最终会找到立足点，并在其他地方寻找新的灵感、新的洞察力和更深的爱。”</p><p>由汉娜·勒克斯·戴维斯（ <a href="/artists/ariana-grande">Ariana Grande</a> 、 <a href="/artists/doja-cat">Doja Cat</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Nicki-Minaj">Nicki Minaj</a> ）执导，这首歌的伴奏视频以马斯格雷夫斯躺在草地上俯瞰大海开始。她还坐在厨房里唱歌，绕着一座小山散步，周围有漂浮的岩石。 </p><figure id="attachment_3584631" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3584631" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3584631" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kacey-Musgraves-Deeper-Well-album-artwork.jpg" alt="凯西·马斯格雷夫斯《Deeper Well》专辑封面" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kacey-Musgraves-Deeper-Well-album-artwork.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kacey-Musgraves-Deeper-Well-album-artwork-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kacey-Musgraves-Deeper-Well-album-artwork-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kacey-Musgraves-Deeper-Well-album-artwork-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kacey-Musgraves-Deeper-Well-album-artwork-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kacey-Musgraves-Deeper-Well-album-artwork-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kacey-Musgraves-Deeper-Well-album-artwork-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3584631" class="wp-caption-text">凯西·马斯格雷夫斯《Deeper Well》专辑封面</figcaption></figure><p><strong>“更深的井”曲目列表是：</strong></p><p> <strong>1.“红衣主教”</strong><br /> <strong>2.“更深的井”</strong><br /> <strong>3.“好得令人难以置信”</strong><br /> <strong>4.“搬出去”</strong><br /> <strong>5.“给予者/接受者”</strong><br /> <strong>6.“摇摆”</strong><br /> <strong>7.《与朋友共进晚餐》</strong><br /> <strong>8.《森林之心》</strong><br /> <strong>9.“翡翠绿”</strong><br /> <strong>10.《建筑师》</strong><br /> <strong>11.《孤独的百万富翁》</strong><br /> <strong>12.《天堂是》</strong><br /> <strong>13.“动漫眼睛”</strong><br /> <strong>14.“没什么好害怕的”</strong></p><p> 《Deeper Well》是她 2021 年专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/kacey-musgraves-star-crossed-review-3040734">Star-Crossed</a> 》之后的作品。 <em>《NME》</em>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/kacey-musgraves-star-crossed-review-3040734">对该专辑的四星评论</a>中表示：“这张唱片以其多样的声音和残酷诚实的歌词，从未发现马斯格雷夫斯回避了不舒服的地方。这是一个复杂的项目——这张唱片还附有一部 50 分钟的电影——可能会在其概念的重压下崩溃。然而，在作者坦率的笔下，并灌输了希望感，这是一次强有力的聆听。”</p><p>该专辑包含歌曲“Camera Roll”，这首歌使马斯格雷夫斯获得了 2021 年格莱美奖最佳乡村歌曲和最佳乡村独奏表演的提名。</p><p>今年，这位六届格莱美奖得主在她的收藏中又增添了一座奖杯——与扎克·布莱恩 (Zach Bryan) 合作的歌曲《我记得一切》(I Remember Everything) 荣获最佳乡村二人组/团体表演奖</p><p>凯西<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kacey-musgraves-announces-new-album-deeper-well-and-shares-leads-single-3584616">·穆斯格雷夫斯 (Kacey Musgraves) 宣布新专辑《Deeper Well》并分享​​主打单曲后，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
